GENERAL QUALITY STANDARDS FOR ALL SUPPLEMENTS

LOOK FOR:
✓ Third-party testing (NSF, USP, ConsumerLab, NSF Certified for Sport)
✓ GMP (Good Manufacturing Practice) certified
✓ Clear, complete ingredient list
✓ Expiration date 12+ months away
✓ Sealed, unopened packaging
✓ Amazon "Fulfilled by Amazon" (quality control)
✓ 4.5+ star customer ratings
✓ Recent verified purchases in reviews

AVOID:
✗ Proprietary blends (you can't verify amounts)
✗ Artificial colors or flavors
✗ Excess fillers (cellulose, silica, magnesium stearate)
✗ Unknown manufacturers
✗ Suspiciously cheap prices (red flag for quality)
✗ Claims like "cure diabetes" (illegal)
✗ Products without expiration dates

STORAGE TIPS:
• Keep in original containers (best protection)
• Cool, dry place away from sunlight
• Avoid bathroom (humidity damages supplements)
• Check monthly for color changes, odors, clumping
• Discard if past expiration date
• Keep out of reach of children

