IMPORTANT WARNINGS & INTERACTIONS

BERBERINE INTERACTIONS:
⚠ May interact with antibiotics (space 2 hours apart)
⚠ Can affect glucose medications (consult doctor)
⚠ May cause GI upset (start low, build up)
⚠ Not recommended during pregnancy

CINNAMON INTERACTIONS:
⚠ High doses (>6g/day) may cause liver stress (stick to 1-2g)
⚠ May thin blood (consult if on blood thinners)

CHROMIUM INTERACTIONS:
⚠ May affect insulin medications (monitor closely)
⚠ Can interact with some medications (tell your doctor)

ALPHA-LIPOIC ACID:
⚠ May cause nausea, headache (usually temporary)
⚠ Can affect blood sugar medications
⚠ Take on empty stomach for best absorption

ALWAYS:
✓ Tell your doctor ALL supplements you're taking
✓ Start with one supplement at a time (to monitor effects)
✓ Give each supplement 4-6 weeks before assessing results
✓ Monitor blood sugar regularly (watch for lows)
✓ Don't stop diabetes medications without doctor approval

